OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely fine with sunny spells,
OL,6,Fmost prolonged in the far west. Cloud
OL,7,Fspreading southwards could bring
OL,8,Fisolated showers in the north and east
OL,9,Fto start with. Moderate showers in
OL,10,FWales and the southwest later, that
OL,11,Fmay turn thundery. Less hot.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers will fade leaving
OL,14,Fa dry and mostly clear night to come.
OL,15,FSome patchy cloud but light winds
OL,16,Fexpected. A cooler night than of
OL,17,Flater, slightly in the southwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
