OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FPatchy cloud to start across
OL,6,Fthe midlands. This lifts to a bright
OL,7,Fand sunny Sunday. Isolated showers in
OL,8,FCornwall and northern Scotland where
OL,9,Fit'll be cloudier. Staying warm for
OL,10,Fmost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
